---
// FooterSection.astro - Contact CTA and copyright
---

<footer id="contact" class="relative min-h-[50vh] bg-itsees-bg flex items-center justify-center pt-80 pb-20">
  <div class="section-container text-center relative z-20">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-itsees-text leading-none tracking-tighter mb-6" style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 9vw, 9rem);">
      Ready to build<br />something?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-itsees-text/80 mb-8 max-w-xs mx-auto">
      Let's turn your vision into reality. Reach out and let's start the conversation.
    </p>
    <a
      href="mailto:hello@itsees.dev"
      class="cta-btn inline-flex items-center gap-2 pl-8 pr-8 py-4 bg-itsees-orange text-itsees-dark rounded-full text-lg font-medium"
    >
      Get in touch
      <svg class="cta-arrow w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
      </svg>
    </a>

    <div class="mt-20 pt-8 border-t border-itsees-text/10">
      <p class="text-itsees-text/40 text-sm">
        &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} itsees. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .cta-btn {
    transition: padding-right 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
  }

  .cta-arrow {
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
  }

  .cta-btn:hover {
    padding-right: 3.5rem;
  }

  .cta-btn:hover .cta-arrow {
    transform: translateX(10px);
  }
</style>
